    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Settle and Battle: New Empires </strong>is a homage to classic real-time strategy games. Gather raw resources, build a thriving empire and command powerful armies. Your ultimate goal: defeat your opponents and conquer the world. Play with up to 8 players</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay 💎</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lead Seven Unique Tribes:</strong> Command one of six distinct tribes, each with their own challenging campaign, distinctive buildings and special units</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Conquer and Unlock:</strong> Defeat your enemies to unlock powerful abilities and expand your empire's potential.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maps and Missions:</strong> Test your skills in 18 thrilling missions, or dive into procedurally generated maps for limitless replayability and own challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer:</strong> Play with up to 8 players. Face off against your mates or ally with them to take on the AI.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/e3d2e5ad98211d0277377e8dd657f776.poster.avif?t=1745837774\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/e3d2e5ad98211d0277377e8dd657f776.webm?t=1745837774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/e3d2e5ad98211d0277377e8dd657f776.mp4?t=1745837774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Economy ⚒️</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand Your Territory:</strong> Claim rich lands and expand your empire to secure a steady flow of resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build a Thriving Kingdom:</strong> Strategically manage resources and optimize complex production chains to ensure prosperity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost Your Economy:</strong> Produce optional goods to increase your settlers productivity and drive economic growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/80798705a9599d8f1627761cded99eaf.poster.avif?t=1745837774\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/80798705a9599d8f1627761cded99eaf.webm?t=1745837774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/80798705a9599d8f1627761cded99eaf.mp4?t=1745837774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat ⚔️</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Recruit a Mighty Army:</strong> Raise a diverse force of soldiers, each with unique strengths and weaknesses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engage in Epic Battles:</strong> Command massive armies and outmaneuver your opponents in large-scale conflicts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destroy and Conquer:</strong> Lay siege to enemy cities, raze their defenses, and claim their territory as your own.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battlefield:</strong> Engage in large-scale conflicts with hundreds of units on the screen</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/90497b4253bdbe695a8a3515c0972281.poster.avif?t=1745837774\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/90497b4253bdbe695a8a3515c0972281.webm?t=1745837774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306790/extras/90497b4253bdbe695a8a3515c0972281.mp4?t=1745837774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
